{"TopicId":145303,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to move to empty seat in IVA?","CreatedByName":"THX1138","CreatedById":113955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T10:44:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"THX1138","CreatedById":113955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T10:44:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to move to an empty seat in IVA? I want to access the controls.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UHnnGTu.png\u0022 alt=\u0022UHnnGTu.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-03T10:44:48Z\u0022 title=\u002208/03/2016 10:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by THX1138\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T12:50:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\npress the button for alternate views. This also switches views in IVA. Usually, this is V\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T13:32:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEVA that Kerbal and bring them right back on board. The command seat always gets filled first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T14:19:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo answer your question: No, you can not switch to an empty seat.\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut you can fill that seat exactly as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57258-jack-wolfe/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002257258\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57258-jack-wolfe/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Jack Wolfe\u003C/a\u003E said. EVA the Kerbal and re-enter the capsule.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dafidge9898","CreatedById":147547,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T15:51:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222702748\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145303\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470228647\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160994\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022qzgy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, qzgy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\npress the button for alternate views. This also switches views in IVA. Usually, this is V\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou just helped two people with that. I had no idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"THX1138","CreatedById":113955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T16:16:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222702748\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145303\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470228647\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160994\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022qzgy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, qzgy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\npress the button for alternate views. This also switches views in IVA. Usually, this is V\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat only works if the other seat is already occupied.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-03T17:27:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222702993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145303\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470240994\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022THX1138\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, THX1138 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat only works if the other seat is already occupied.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk. Usually, all my seats are occupied, so I did not know\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}